Actuator-Health check

In appliaction.properties file
-------------------------------
management.endpoint.health.show-details=always
management.endpoints.web.exposure.include=*

In pom.xml file-add build-info in maven plugin
------------------
			<plugin>
				<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
				<artifactId>spring-boot-maven-plugin</artifactId>
				<executions>
					<execution>
						<goals>
							<goal>build-info</goal>
						</goals>
					</execution>
				</executions>
			</plugin>
			
		<dependency>
			<groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
			<artifactId>spring-boot-actuator</artifactId>
		</dependency>

Some endpoints
---------------
http://localhost:8080/productapi/actuator
http://localhost:8080/productapi/actuator/health
http://localhost:8080/productapi/actuator/env
http://localhost:8080/productapi/actuator/info
http://localhost:8080/productapi/actuator/metrics
http://localhost:8080/productapi/actuator/beans

springfox-swagger version 3.0.0 and spring boot starter version 2.6.0 issues

resolved

http://localhost:8080/productapi/swagger-ui.html
http://localhost:8080/productapi/v2/api-docs

springfox-swagger version 2.9.2 and spring boot starter version 2.6.0


for swagger configuration

pom.xml

springfox-swagger2
springfox-swagger-ui

@SpringBootApplication
@EnableSwagger2
public class HellospringbootApplication {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		SpringApplication.run(HellospringbootApplication.class, args);
	}
